---

<section class="py-20 sm:py-24 md:py-32 px-4 sm:px-6 relative overflow-hidden bg-slate-50/50">
    <!-- Subtle dividers -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-slate-200 to-transparent"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-slate-200 to-transparent"></div>
    
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10">
        <!-- Section Header -->
        <div 
            class="text-center mb-14 sm:mb-16 md:mb-20"
            data-animate="fade-up"
        >
            <span class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-red-50 border border-red-100 text-red-600 text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium tracking-wide uppercase mb-5">
                El Problema
            </span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-5 sm:mb-6">
                ¿Tu personal está <span class="text-red-500">saturado</span>?
            </h2>
            <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                La gestión manual de pacientes está costando dinero y reputación a tu clínica
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Problem Cards - Soft shadows, white background -->
        <div 
            class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 sm:gap-8"
            data-animate-stagger
        >
            <!-- Card 1: Llamadas Perdidas -->
            <div 
                class="bg-white rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl p-6 sm:p-8 group hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm"
                data-animate="fade-up"
            >
                <!-- Icon container -->
                <div class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 bg-red-50 rounded-xl sm:rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 sm:mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-red-100 transition-all duration-300">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 sm:w-7 sm:h-7 text-red-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M16 8l2-2m0 0l2-2m-2 2l-2-2m2 2l2 2M5 3a2 2 0 00-2 2v1c0 8.284 6.716 15 15 15h1a2 2 0 002-2v-3.28a1 1 0 00-.684-.948l-4.493-1.498a1 1 0 00-1.21.502l-1.13 2.257a11.042 11.042 0 01-5.516-5.517l2.257-1.128a1 1 0 00.502-1.21L9.228 3.683A1 1 0 008.279 3H5z"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Content -->
                <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-slate-900 group-hover:text-red-600 transition-colors">
                    Llamadas Perdidas
                </h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base mb-6" style="line-height: 1.65;">
                    El <span class="text-red-500 font-semibold">60%</span> de los pacientes llaman fuera de horario laboral. Si no respondes al instante, llaman a la competencia.
                </p>
                
                <!-- Stat highlight - elevated card feel -->
                <div class="pt-5 border-t border-slate-100">
                    <div class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-red-500">-29%</div>
                    <div class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-400 mt-1">Pérdida promedio de ingresos</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 2: Ausentismo -->
            <div 
                class="bg-white rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl p-6 sm:p-8 group hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm"
                data-animate="fade-up"
            >
                <div class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 bg-orange-50 rounded-xl sm:rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 sm:mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-orange-100 transition-all duration-300">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 sm:w-7 sm:h-7 text-orange-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 14l2 2 4-4"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                
                <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-slate-900 group-hover:text-orange-600 transition-colors">
                    Ausentismo Alto
                </h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base mb-6" style="line-height: 1.65;">
                    Pacientes que olvidan su cita por falta de confirmación inmediata, dejando huecos imposibles de llenar.
                </p>
                
                <div class="pt-5 border-t border-slate-100">
                    <div class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-orange-500">15-25%</div>
                    <div class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-400 mt-1">Tasa de no-show promedio</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 3: Tareas Repetitivas -->
            <div 
                class="bg-white rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl p-6 sm:p-8 group hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm sm:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1"
                data-animate="fade-up"
            >
                <div class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 bg-amber-50 rounded-xl sm:rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 sm:mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-amber-100 transition-all duration-300">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 sm:w-7 sm:h-7 text-amber-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                
                <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-slate-900 group-hover:text-amber-600 transition-colors">
                    Tareas Repetitivas
                </h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base mb-6" style="line-height: 1.65;">
                    Tu equipo pierde horas respondiendo "¿Cuánto cuesta?" y "¿Dónde están?" una y otra vez.
                </p>
                
                <div class="pt-5 border-t border-slate-100">
                    <div class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-amber-500">4+ hrs</div>
                    <div class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-400 mt-1">Tiempo perdido por día</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
